{"type": "article", "id": 9675, "title": "“Body Building” 创意展示", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-18T07:23:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235641Uhcvnsx6GXtV2Qyk.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t设计师 Alberto Biagetti 和 Laura Baldassari 联手推出了一个名为 “Body Building” 的创意展示，以此庆祝今年的米兰设计周。在展览里面，客厅里面的长凳原型为传统的鞍马，结合了马皮和海狸毛，而咖啡桌的支撑则是哑铃，体操环被伪装成了灯饰。传统的健身项目和现代化的设计紧密结合在一起。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052356399EuaJMSvxq1QPdKT.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235640rQ01ueBYOSP4IUFd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523564071PpyLa8SMETHJor.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235640OT0JVKbm2CogNYtP.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}